  "body": "<p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fcgwZZjIG8c\"><strong>Watch on YouTube</strong></a> </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>The Alternative Rain Sounds</strong> resource pack replaces the default sounds for rain and thunder with more realistic and atmospheric sounds. Now the rain sounds much more then defoult minecraft sounds. The thunder is also updated, with a more dramatic and powerful sounds. With this resource pack, you'll be able to immerse yourself in the game even more. I hope you'll enjoy it :)</span></p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><strong>FAQ:</strong></span></h2>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Anyone can use this resource pack in their mod pack.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Licenses and original sounds:</span></li>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">\n<a href=\"remoteUrl=https%253a%252f%252fpixabay.com%252fsound-effects%252fnatural-thunder-113219%252f\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://pixabay.com/sound-effects/rain-and-thunder-nature-sounds-7803/</a></span><br>\n<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">\n<a href=\"remoteUrl=https%253a%252f%252fpixabay.com%252fsound-effects%252fnatural-thunder-113219%252f\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://pixabay.com/sound-effects/soft-rain-ambient-111154/</a></span><br>\n<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">\n<a href=\"remoteUrl=https%253a%252f%252fpixabay.com%252fsound-effects%252fnatural-thunder-113219%252f\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://pixabay.com/sound-effects/natural-thunder-113219/</a></span><br>\n<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">\n<a href=\"remoteUrl=https%253a%252f%252ffreesound.org%252fpeople%252fbone666138%252fsounds%252f198857%252f\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://freesound.org/people/bone666138/sounds/198857/</a></span><br>\n<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">\n<a href=https%253a%252f%252fpixabay.com%252fsound-effects%252fthunder-24571%252f\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://pixabay.com/sound-effects/thunder-24571/</a></span></p>",
